      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior finish remains vibrant and glossy, though a close inspection may reveal a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with all electronics and features functioning as intended. Mechanically, it remains strong and reliable, offering a smooth and dependable driving experience for its next owner.",
